{"title":"Larkin Cycles Los Angeles Fire Relief Fundraiser","link":"https://theradavist.com/larkin-cycles-los-angeles-fire-relief-fundraiser/","date":1739217473000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-11.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-11.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Darren Larkin from <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/larkin-cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Larkin Cycles</a> has teamed up with a number of companies to pull together <a href=\"http://larkincycles.com/fundraiser\" target=\"_blank\">a stunning fundraiser bike for Los Angeles fire relief</a>. Read on for Larkin Cycles’ project description and <a href=\"https://ronsbikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Ron’s Bikes</a> photo documentation of this <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/beautiful-bicycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Beautiful Bicycle</a>…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-1.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-3.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-3.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>You’re all aware that there were multiple wildfires in the Los Angeles area that moved uncontrolled through dense neighborhoods, destroying hundreds of homes and many lives. It’s a devastating situation for the people directly involved and a huge strain on the fabric of many wider communities.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-7.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-7.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>So, along with some great friends and sponsors, we organized this little bike giveaway in hopes that it could rustle up some more donations to help people rebuild.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-2.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-2.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-12.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-12.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The frame is a fillet-brazed flat bar adventure gravel bike with a loud throw-back custom paint job from <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/probikedesign/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Pro Bike Design</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/N405DF-Grumman-S-2F-Tracker_01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/N405DF-Grumman-S-2F-Tracker_01.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/N405DF-Grumman-S-2F-Tracker_01.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/N405DF-Grumman-S-2F-Tracker_01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/N405DF-Grumman-S-2F-Tracker_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/N405DF-Grumman-S-2F-Tracker_02.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/N405DF-Grumman-S-2F-Tracker_02.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/N405DF-Grumman-S-2F-Tracker_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The paint job itself was inspired by the old Mountain Goat Whiskeytown Racers – <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/1984-mountain-goat-whiskeytown-racer-2/\" target=\"_blank\">like what John has</a> – which were inspired by the N405DF Grumman S-2F Tracker firefighter planes from the 1970s and 1980s in a serendipitous and completely unintended homage to California’s history of combating fires.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-14.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-14.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-14.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-14.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Geometry:</strong></p>\n<p>Effective Top Tube = 56.5cm<br />\nStandover = 83cm<br />\nStack = 59cm<br />\nReach = 39.5cm<br />\nTire clearance = 700 x 2.3″</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-5.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-5.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-6.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-6.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Larkin_Cycles_LA_Fire_Fundraiser_Bike-6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Parts List</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://astralcycling.com/products/outback-wheel-set\" target=\"_blank\">Astral Cycling Outback wheelset</a> with <a href=\"https://www.whiteind.com/\" target=\"_blank\">White Industries</a> CLD hubs</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brooksengland.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Brooks</a> C17 saddle</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1ee84457-7e2e-498d-87ed-ecb578e5c230&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fchrisking.com%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Chris King</a> headset and bottom bracket</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crustbikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Crust Bikes</a> x Nitto handlesbars, stem, seatpost, etc.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.paulcomp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Component Engineering</a> Klamper flat mount brakes and Love levers</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://bike.shimano.com/home.html\" target=\"_blank\">Shimano</a> Deore XT Linkglide 1×11 geartrain and shifteR</li>\n<li>Shimano Deore XT 11-50 Cassette</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ultradynamico.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Ultradynamico</a> Mars tires 700 x 2.3″</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.whiteind.com/\" target=\"_blank\">White Industries</a> G30 crankset with 36T Chainring</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Support this fundraiser at <a href=\"http://larkincycles.com/fundraiser\" target=\"_blank\">Larkin Cycles</a>.</strong></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/larkin-cycles-los-angeles-fire-relief-fundraiser/\">Larkin Cycles Los Angeles Fire Relief Fundraiser</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"63b9a55f931f03fdfe9f9f9ece76d9bce6bc80155bd2d002a30d03371e591c3b","category":"Cycling"}